graph TD
%% Initial Feed Creation
A[User Inputs URL] --> B{Automatic Analysis}
B -->|Success| C[Generate Feed Config]
B -->|Failure| D[Manual Selection Interface]
D --> C
C --> E[Store Feed Config]

    %% Update Process
    E --> F[Update Manager]
    F --> G{Check Update Time}
    G -->|Due| H[Fetch Website]
    G -->|Not Due| F

    H --> I[Extract Content]
    I --> J{Detect Changes}

    %% Change Detection
    J -->|No Changes| K[Update Next Check Time]
    J -->|Changes Found| L[Process New Content]
    L --> M[Update Feed]
    M --> N[Store New Items]
    N --> K

    K --> F

    %% Error Handling
    H -->|Error| O[Error Handler]
    O -->|Temporary| P[Queue for Retry]
    O -->|Permanent| Q[Notify User]
    P --> F

    %% Subprocesses
    subgraph "Change Detection"
    R[Compare Hashes]
    S[Check URLs/GUIDs]
    T[Content Similarity]
    R & S & T --> J
    end

    subgraph "Content Processing"
    U[Normalize Content]
    V[Generate Hashes]
    W[Extract Metadata]
    U --> V --> W
    end

    style A fill:#d0f4de
    style F fill:#ffcfd2
    style J fill:#f1c0e8
    style M fill:#cfbaf0
